<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        body {
            height: 100vh !important;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Taskist</title>
</head>
<body class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-5">
    <div class="card w-25 mb-5">
        <h5 class="card-header">Atenção</h5>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text">Você já está autenticado como <%= username %></p>
          <p class="card-text">Você precisa sair para então entrar como outro usuário.</p>
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
              <a href="/auth/logout?next=<%= next %>" class="btn btn-danger m-2">Sair</a>
              <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary m-2">Cancelar</a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>